(23, 7, 'whyAlpha2.0', '<div style="all: unset;width: 100%;"><p>I Alfa Electrical</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>iAlpha company founded in the early eighties of the last century by Ahmed Abdel Hafez in Egypt, and since the company was founded and we are developing and trying to get a privileged position in the electrical products market.</p>\r\n<p>Our company is characterized by advanced manufacturing tools and quality standards and high accuracy during the industry, enabling us to offer the best service and highest quality products at the best prices.</p>\r\n<p>The company owns six shows and Mall of electric tools in the Egyptian capital of Cairo, also have two factories in Ismailia and Qantara, as we are at the moment to build a plant on a 5,000 square meter area and the headquarters has an area of ​​1,200 square meters in the industrial zone in New Cairo.</p>\r\n<p>Every employee in the company is working assiduously to ensure the company''s ability to meet all the needs of the market of electrical products, whether services to the population or even commercial services.</p>\r\n<p>Privileged position in the company iAlpha our faith and confidence in our capabilities, nothing is difficult for us to do with work and diligence. In order to transfer that confidence also for our clients, customers ensure their full rights in the event of dissatisfaction with the services provided by the company, and can recover unpaid financial value by 100%.</p>\r\n<p>We are happy to meet the needs of services and electrical products, your comfort is the first priority.</p></div>', '<div style="all: unset;width: 100%;direction: rtl;"><h1 style="text-align: right;">I Alfa Electrical</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">أُسست شركة iAlpha في بداية ثمانينات القرن الماضي من قبل المهندس أحمد عبد الحافظ في مصر، ومنذ تأسيس الشركة ونحن نتطور ونسعى للحصول على مكانة متميزة في سوق المنتجات الكهربية.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">تتميّز شركتنا بأدوا