(30, 13, 'Repairing_Outlets01', '<div style="all: unset;width: 100%;"><h2><strong>Repairing Outlets</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Our repair experts from Alpha are here ready to offer help with outlet repair to fix all those flickering lights. Alpha is here to meet your electrical repair needs. If ever your outlet at home is not working, it could mean an even serious issue. Call our company and let our repair specialists today what the issue is all about.</p>\r\n<p>We are an insured and licensed electrical contractor with experience and knowledge in the electrical repair. You can rely on us to help you fix your electrical issues and provide you only the most affordable solutions to handle the issue.</p>\r\n<p>Our service extends to both commercial and residential properties no matter how big or small the project is.&nbsp; Put our certified electricians to the test to help you more with your outlet problems. Included in the repair service is a point-by-point inspection of all outlets. Apart from it, the most practical solutions will be presented to you to fully restore your electrical system back to its good condition.</p>\r\n<p>In any situation of your outlet, it will be fixed and repaired just to meet your requests. We will also do everything from special outlets, 3 prong outlets and larger appliances like electric dryers, dishwashers and other outlets that are usually found in the bathrooms and kitchens. No matter what type of outlet that you utilize for your business interior or home interior, we have the knowledge and the skill to carry out the routine repair of outlets.</p>\r\n<p>If ever you have decided to ask help for the repair of outlets at home, discuss the circumstances you have with our electrician as you budget and plan for your project. Our electrician will do the necessary repairs to the wiring and receptacle and additional repairs to help correct the damages.</p>\r\n<p>There is simply no need to hesitate in getting your outlet repaired by our team. It is best 